title: [Gyldemar Green, Forest]
description: The path winds down to the northeast and climbs towards denser foliage to the south.  Far to the north you glimpse a ridge rising through the trees, in the dim moonlight.  A feral growl is carried on the wind, sending a chill down your spine.
